        <item>
            <title>「微信保險」騙案新進展，警方拘捕上門收取騙款 15 歲男童</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/21/wechat-scam-2/tech-secure/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=wechat-scam-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/21/wechat-scam-2/tech-secure/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 12:00:33 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[城中熱話]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[資訊保安]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[微信保險]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[詐騙電話]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1257618</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">最近不少人都收到了騙徒冒充成微信客服的詐騙電話和短訊，警方最近就接獲了一名 54 歲男子的報案，指自己遇到了「微信保險」騙案並被騙去 82 萬和信用卡，最後更成功將騙徒拘捕。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">受害人當日收到了騙徒冒充成微信客服的電話，指他所申請的微信保險計劃將每月自動扣費。他表示自己未有申請相關服務，騙徒聲稱可幫助他取消保險的自動扣賬，並能安排同夥前往住所提供技術支援。受害人向騙徒透露住址，並將信用卡交給對方和把 82 萬元轉帳至騙徒户口，事後與家人交談才意識到自己受騙並報案求助。警方翻查閉路電視片段和深入調查後，成功在黃大仙區以涉嫌「以欺騙手段取得財產」將當日上門收取騙款的 15 歲男童拘捕。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1257622 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/froala_687923114257-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/froala_687923114257-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/froala_687923114257.jpg 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源：<a href="https://www.adcc.gov.hk/zh-hk/alerts-detail/alerts-1819277222420434945.html">反詐騙協調中心</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">警方指出最近「假冒客服」的騙案有上升趨勢，呼籲市民提防受騙，切勿輕易交出個人資料和進行轉帳，一旦懷疑受騙可致電 18222 至警方的「防騙易熱線」。警方指「以欺騙手段取得財產」為嚴重罪行，最高刑罰為監禁十年，呼籲青少年勿因一時貪念而參與犯罪活動。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1257623 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/froala_79119493170-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/froala_79119493170-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/froala_79119493170.jpg 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1257624 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/froala_958737336644-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/froala_958737336644-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/froala_958737336644.jpg 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源：<a href="https://www.adcc.gov.hk/zh-hk/alerts-detail/alerts-1819277222420434945.html">反詐騙協調中心</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2018468/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E8%A8%9B%E7%A8%B1WeChat%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%AE%A2%E6%9C%8D%E5%91%83%E8%B5%B082%E8%90%AC-%E8%AD%A6%E6%8B%98%E4%B8%8A%E9%96%80%E6%94%B6%E9%8C%A215%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E7%AB%A5?fbclid=IwY2xjawEyhSdleHRuA2FlbQIxMAABHQgdDAonXi46R-vEaQ5OhqtL6jww0rZHcz5m0A9rpYJXAnQK5tB0SxsSng_aem_yvgcoA5ir4ckEi-4c9CxoA">星島</a></p><p>圖片來源：<a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1766684-20240819.htm">RTHK</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/08/wechat-scam/tech-secure/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">「微信保險」詐騙電話 Cut 線會打來問原因　連登網民分享對付騙徒新招</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/21/wechat-scam-2/tech-secure/">「微信保險」騙案新進展，警方拘捕上門收取騙款 15 歲男童</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
